caption.title: Quantities of HA and NS1 mRNAs and HA and NS vRNAs in infected DF-1 cells.
caption.p: Cells were infected with the viruses at MOI of 1 and viral mRNA (A) and vRNA (B) were quantitated by qRT-PCR at various times after infection. The data represent averages with standard deviations (n = 3). *, P < 0.05.
